text:
Happy Valentines Day From Ariel Winter’s Butt Cheeks! Trent | Email 

Happy Valentines Day! What a treat. This is for all the single people out there (and the people with a significant other who they hate) who don’t have anybody today. Ariel Winter is here to make our our day super special by showing off dem cheeks. I would like to know how many takes it took to get that specific picture. That’s almost always my question when it comes to hot chicks and Instagram pictures. You don’t post a picture like that unless it’s perfect and that picture happens to be perfect. Just when I think the other Modern Family sister has pulled ahead, the other sister goes and does something like this and totally redeems herself. It’s been a full out arms (and ass cheeks and boobs) race between the two of them for some time now. Keep it rolling ladies.
